Distribution (Windows):
- Data/ (hidden)        Apps' data files
- Annot Browser.exe     App launcher of data/annot-browser.exe
- Annot Downloader.exe  App launcher of data/annot-down.exe
- Annot Player.exe      App launcher of data/annot-player.exe
- ChangeLog.txt         Log of changes (UTF-8)
- COPYING.txt           GPLv3 license
- Read Me.txt           Readme (UTF-8)
- Reset Preferences.reg Remove all registry settings (HKCU/Software/Annot)

